The paper deals with image recognition and retrieval, which suggests that it is likely to belong to the computer vision (cs.CV) sub-category. The use of retrieval techniques and CNN approaches also suggests that it may belong to the information retrieval (cs.IR) and multimedia (cs.MM) sub-categories. The use of ensembling and re-ranking strategies suggests that it may also belong to the machine learning (cs.LG) and natural language processing (cs.CL) sub-categories.
